tellolib.communication

Interface TelloCommunicationInterface

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    TelloCommunication

    public interface TelloCommunicationInterface
    Low level support interface for sending and receiving data from DJI Tello drone.

    • Method Detail

      • connect

        void connect()
        Establish connection to the Tello drone. Creates UDP sockets for sending commands and receiving asynchronous status updates. Pings drone to make sure it is accessible.

      • executeCommand

        void executeCommand(TelloCommandInterface telloCommand)
        Executes command on Tello drone. Waits until timeout for status response.
        Parameters:
        telloCommand - The command to be executed.

      • executeReadCommand

        java.lang.String executeReadCommand(TelloCommandInterface telloCommand)
        Executes command on Tello drone that returns data. Waits until timeout for status response.
        Parameters:
        telloCommand - The command to be executed.
        Returns:
        Data returned from Tello or empty string.

      • executeCommands

        void executeCommands(java.util.List<TelloCommandInterface> telloCommandList)
        Executes a list of commands on Tello drone.
        Parameters:
        telloCommandList - The list of commands to be executed.

      • disconnect

        void disconnect()
        Disconnect from the Tello. Close sockets.

      • getTelloOnBoardData

        java.util.Map<java.lang.String,java.lang.String> getTelloOnBoardData(java.util.List<java.lang.String> valuesToBeObtained)
        Obtains data about the Tello drone.
        Parameters:
        valuesToBeObtained - Values (names) to be obtained from the drone.
        Returns:
        Map of the data.

      • receiveStatusData

        java.lang.String receiveStatusData()
                            throws java.io.IOException
        Returns most recent status packet from the drone when status monitoring is enabled.
        Returns:
        The status data.
        Throws:
        java.io.IOException

      • executeCommandNoWait

        void executeCommandNoWait(TelloCommandInterface telloCommand)
        Executes command on Tello drone. Does not Wait for status response.
        Parameters:
        telloCommand - The command to be executed.
